For <feFuncA>, x defines the minimum x coordinate for the rendering area of the primitive.

  --------------- -------------------------
  Value           <length> | <percentage>
  Default value   0%
  Animatable      Yes
  --------------- -------------------------

<feFuncB>

For <feFuncB>, x defines the minimum x coordinate for the rendering area of the primitive.

